23:16.834 --> 23:20.458
Shouldn't it be that way when it comes to knowing God's word?

23:21.439 --> 23:25.965
Why are we so willing and able to learn a song that catches our attention?

23:26.265 --> 23:33.153
But we are so unwilling to do the same with God's word that was written specifically for us.

23:35.877 --> 23:38.380
We're so willing to fill ourselves with other things.

23:39.341 --> 23:43.826
