24:08.642 --> 24:11.187
We're like, as long as I've got that one in my back pocket, I'm okay.

24:11.408 --> 24:15.316
But I want you to see what it says in Psalm chapter one, verses two and three.

24:15.757 --> 24:28.082
Look what it says about those who believe in God, but they delight, say it with me, but they, in the law of the Lord, meditating on it day and night.

24:28.290 --> 24:32.316
They are like trees planted along the riverbank, bearing fruit in season.

24:32.576 --> 24:36.682
Their leaves never wither and they prosper in all they do.

24:36.743 --> 24:38.745
That word wasn't just for Joshua.

24:39.406 --> 24:44.354
