28:10.630 --> 28:13.673
But Jesus invites us into a radically different way of being.

28:14.133 --> 28:15.154
Where was Mary?

28:16.450 --> 28:19.193
She was sitting at the feet of Jesus.

28:20.354 --> 28:32.727
Not because she was lazy and not because she was irresponsible because she understood the fundamental rule that who you are matters more than what you do.

28:33.809 --> 28:36.692
And where are you going to find out who you are?

28:36.752 --> 28:42.578
You're gonna find out in God's word and you're gonna find it sitting at the feet of Jesus.

28:45.922 --> 28:53.458
When we come to Jesus Christ becomes the foundation from which all of our meaningful actions flow.

28:54.018 --> 28:58.925
When we choose a compartmentalized life, we think we have to choose one or the other.

28:59.285 --> 29:04.252
Either you're the spiritual one who prays, or you're the practical one who's getting things done.

29:04.893 --> 29:11.662
Either you prioritize intimacy with God, or you're out prioritizing action in the world.

29:11.902 --> 29:13.644
How many of us do the same thing?

29:14.165 --> 29:19.011
We read our Bibles, we check the box, we serve at church, so that we feel valuable.

29:19.312 --> 29:24.018
We're doing all the right things, but we're doing them from the wrong place.

29:24.738 --> 29:32.005
And so the idea of sitting in meditation just feels like one more thing that we have to put on our to-do list.

29:34.047 --> 29:44.298
But Jesus invites us to a centered life where everything flows from sitting at his feet and listening to his words and receiving his love.

29:44.578 --> 29:48.782
I'm asking you today, bring your whole self to him.

29:48.842 --> 29:52.306
Not the part of you that wants to perform.

29:52.610 --> 29:55.413
and not the part of you that just wants more knowledge of the Bible.

29:55.433 --> 29:56.094
No, no, no, no, no.

29:56.394 --> 29:57.615
Bring your whole self to him.

29:58.776 --> 30:03.321
All the questions, all the hurt, all the longing, all the misunderstanding.

30:03.622 --> 30:15.274
And as you sit at the speed of Jesus, as you read that verse over and over, as you say it again and again to yourself, study this book of instruction continually, meditate on it day and night.

30:15.894 --> 30:19.378
Then you will be successful and prosper in all you do.

30:20.258 --> 30:23.622
when you say it over and over and over again.

30:23.662 --> 30:38.561
Not only do you receive from the feet of Jesus there, but as you stand up to walk into the rest of your day, into the rest of your relationships, into the rest of your task, into the rest of your life, you are aligned with Jesus.

30:40.383 --> 30:42.205
His invitation is always the same.

30:42.605 --> 30:44.628
Make yourself available.

30:45.689 --> 30:49.554
Sit, listen, meditate,

30:49.794 --> 30:59.326
receive, and from that center place, everything else will flow.

30:59.346 --> 31:00.807
And so I want you to try it this week.

