31:32.598 --> 31:36.561
Read it.

31:38.083 --> 31:38.423
Stop.

31:40.165 --> 31:41.586
Is there a word that comes to mind?

31:42.527 --> 31:44.049
Is there a phrase that comes to mind?

31:45.030 --> 31:46.431
Is there an action I should do?

31:47.612 --> 31:49.554
How will this change me today?

31:51.010 --> 31:51.471
Stop.

31:54.615 --> 31:54.835
Read it.

31:56.378 --> 31:59.342
Trust in the Lord with all your heart.

32:00.724 --> 32:09.997
Lay not on your own understanding, in all your ways, acknowledge Him, and He will show you which path to take.

32:10.057 --> 32:13.602
Is there a word that stands out?

32:14.704 --> 32:16.366
Is there a phrase that speaks to me?

32:16.406 --> 32:18.930
Is there an action I need to do?

32:20.258 --> 32:25.487
How is this verse going to change my heart and my life today?

32:28.371 --> 32:32.458
The Bible is God's love letter and instruction manual and guide for our lives.

32:33.920 --> 32:39.890
When we meditate, we hear the Word of God speak.

